WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
BERMUDA TO NOVA SCOTIA.
50 FOOT SLOOP STRANGE SITUATIONS, WHITE HULL,
THREE PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE BERMUDA
(32-18.47N 064-45.03W) TO NOVA SCOTIA
(44-40.92N 063-44.66W). VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
